ğŸ” Category 3: Authentication & Identity

This governs how users access, prove identity, and manage permissions â€” across devices, sessions, and roles.
---

STRUCTURE

1. ğŸ”¹ Core Auth Flows (Frontend + Backend)
2. ğŸ”¸ Session & Token Management
